findings.title: add function issue
findings.description: If some LP token is added to the contract twice using function add, then the total amount of reward in function updatePool will be incorrect.

findings.title: Owner privileges
findings.description: Fee setter can change the transfer fee and add addresses to the whitelist in PancakeForkToken token. Owner of PancakeForkMasterChef can change deposit fee and withdraw fee before and after 10 days.
